g":"咩片？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:00:23.000Z","msg":"格雷50"},{"pid":"3e3b9b8a23ab98da9a2cbd11763ad07d66e66acd","tid":729979,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9e5b52ea0ec3458f0df64f0050bba46ea28485","tid":729979,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"倒數最後一小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac35d6e02865ef7adcefb5d3e6a411015b96bfd","tid":729979,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b9e5b52ea0ec3458f0df64f0050bba46ea28485","tid":729979,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"倒數最後一小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"已經7月6日啦<br />\n<br />\n依家點?"},{"pid":"9f96c63575b9a2caf4238880b6518ce35fff7819","tid":729979,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7dd21e5eeb6172095e535c1e182beb338e3594","tid":729979,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"6號啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751963f32817ac901a39c9a5bc0257a43a87e86a","tid":729979,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ac35d6e02865ef7adcefb5d3e6a411015b96bfd","tid":729979,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b9e5b52ea0ec3458f0df64f0050bba46ea28485","tid":729979,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"倒數最後一小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"已經7月6日啦<br />\n<br />\n依家點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要等美國徵稅先喎<br />\n<br />\n【中方不會開第一槍】<br />\n【商務部：美國向全世界以及自己開火】<br />\n【環時：美國遏制中國因中國強大】<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰星期五正式開打，中方即將面對一個問題是：誰先出手？<br />\n<br />\n北京與華盛頓有十二小時的時差，若北京在星期五00:01宣布關稅生效，華盛頓仍是星期四中午，變相由中方掀起貿易戰。所以中方表示，反制措施會在美方加稅後才生效，換言之貿易戰最快在北京時間星期五12:01開打。<br />\n<br />\n商務部表明，中方決不開第一槍，但為了維護國家和人民利益，不得不打，如果美方實施徵稅措施，中方將被迫進行反制。商務部又表示，被美國徵稅的340億美元產品中，有近六成都是由外資企業生產的，當中美資企業亦佔了相當比例，形容美國是在向全世界及自己開火。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報社評表示，美國之所以遏制中國是因為中國強大，所以中國不用驚慌，要有面對曲折的平常心。社評又指中國前數年過得太順利，一直沒有真正的表現機會，現在打貿易戰大家反而更踏實，對國家的承受力亦建立信心。<br />\n<br />\n#貿易戰<br />\n#第一槍<br />\n#敵不動我不動<br />\n#有線中國組"}]}